  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State \nconsiders that there are \nreasonable grounds to suspect that DALIAN UNITECH TRADING CO., LTD. is and has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine by providing economic resources, goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n",
